665
00:31:34,270 --> 00:31:34,730
Okay?

666
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:39,460
Give me my things!

667
00:31:45,310 --> 00:31:46,380
You're back.

668
00:31:46,710 --> 00:31:47,510
Where's our son?

669
00:31:47,950 --> 00:31:50,420
H-He's still in detention.

670
00:31:50,630 --> 00:31:52,650
What were you doing?

671
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:54,910
