00:32:33,550 --> 00:32:34,470
You should stay at home.

686
00:32:34,490 --> 00:32:35,430
Granny Ma.

687
00:32:35,470 --> 00:32:36,390
Careful, careful.

688
00:32:36,410 --> 00:32:37,870
