689
00:32:37,890 --> 00:32:38,630
Have a seat.

690
00:32:38,630 --> 00:32:39,760
Careful, careful.

691
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:42,010
Alright.

692
00:32:42,060 --> 00:32:43,270
