700
00:32:57,110 --> 00:32:58,030
The principal thinks

701
00:32:58,060 --> 00:32:59,650
what Wanghe did is understandable,

702
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:01,370
but he doesn't encourage

703
00:33:01,390 --> 00:33:02,160
or support his behavior.

704
00:33:02,350 --> 00:33:03,150
Gosh,

705
00:33:03,180 --> 00:33:05,020
