706
00:33:05,040 --> 00:33:06,670
Officer Shen just called.

707
00:33:06,690 --> 00:33:08,930
The police station is planning

708
00:33:08,970 --> 00:33:10,360
to arrange a mediation tomorrow.

709
00:33:10,390 --> 00:33:12,120
