710
00:33:12,790 --> 00:33:13,950
Conditions?

711
00:33:14,250 --> 00:33:16,170
I went to the hospital to see that guy.

712
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:17,450
He's a tough nut to crack.

713
00:33:17,470 --> 00:33:18,940
He won't settle this with us peacefully.

714
00:33:18,980 --> 00:33:20,600
That bastard started it!

715
00:33:20,630 --> 00:33:21,700
Shut up!

716
00:33:21,740 --> 00:33:22,500
It's true.

717
00:33:22,520 --> 00:33:23,220
Xingchi.

718
00:33:23,260 --> 00:33:24,420
It is true.

719
00:33:24,440 --> 00:33:25,490
That guy

720
00:33:26,230 --> 00:33:27,910
photoshopped Fenghua's underwear photos

721
00:33:27,950 --> 00:33:29,030
