727
00:33:35,140 --> 00:33:35,880
Calm down.

728
00:33:35,910 --> 00:33:36,430
Wait.

729
00:33:36,430 --> 00:33:37,030
Make it clear.

730
00:33:37,070 --> 00:33:37,950
Here's what happened.

731
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:38,720
Well,

732
00:33:38,740 --> 00:33:39,620
