738
00:33:45,270 --> 00:33:46,630
So he beat that guy up.

739
00:33:46,790 --> 00:33:48,220
Zhou Haikuo, why didn't you…

740
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:50,610
Why didn't you tell us this earlier?

741
00:33:50,670 --> 00:33:51,710
Who do you think you are?

742
00:33:51,740 --> 00:33:54,810
You think you can handle this by yourselves?

743
00:33:54,990 --> 00:33:56,030
What should we do?

744
00:33:56,070 --> 00:33:57,230
