745
00:33:57,270 --> 00:33:58,620
Don't panic, don't panic.

746
00:33:58,670 --> 00:33:59,860
What's the situation now?

747
00:33:59,900 --> 00:34:00,610
Where are the photos?

748
00:34:00,640 --> 00:34:01,290
We discovered it early

749
00:34:01,310 --> 00:34:01,910
