750
00:34:01,990 --> 00:34:02,550
They've already been deleted.

751
00:34:02,570 --> 00:34:03,680
The school has intervened.

752
00:34:03,750 --> 00:34:04,500
Are you sure they're deleted?

753
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:05,350
Yes, yes.

754
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:08,560
So Wanghe did this for Fenghua!

755
00:34:08,699 --> 00:34:09,820
You guys,

756
00:34:10,030 --> 00:34:11,889
