757
00:34:11,949 --> 00:34:12,949
Wanghe went on his own.

758
00:34:12,949 --> 00:34:13,790
He didn't tell us.

759
00:34:13,790 --> 00:34:15,550
We both only found out afterward.

760
00:34:15,600 --> 00:34:17,340
How did you know it was that guy?

761
00:34:17,980 --> 00:34:18,630
Yeah.

762
00:34:18,650 --> 00:34:19,290
