767
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:30,230
But I think

768
00:34:30,250 --> 00:34:32,830
he's the one who took the original photos.

769
00:34:32,850 --> 00:34:33,850
That's a clue.

770
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:36,520
But we need to file a police report first.

771
00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:37,150
Report it to the police!

772
00:34:37,179 --> 00:34:37,770
We must report it to the police!

773
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:38,679
He should be arrested!

774
00:34:38,900 --> 00:34:40,070
Will that help?

775
00:34:40,100 --> 00:34:41,300
This isn't evidence.

776
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:43,120
Can you prove he broke the law?

777
00:34:43,159 --> 00:34:44,830
He was just trying to give us trouble.

778
00:34:46,290 --> 00:34:47,330
Wait.

779
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:50,120
Isn't the boy still detained?

780
00:34:50,139 --> 00:34:52,219
Let's get him out

781
00:34:52,250 --> 00:34:54,100
before discussing other matters, okay?

782
00:34:54,120 --> 00:34:55,040
Yes, yes.

783
00:34:55,070 --> 00:34:55,949
Let's get him out first.

784
00:34:55,969 --> 00:34:57,170
He's the most important now.

785
00:34:57,200 --> 00:34:57,690
Right.

786
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:58,590
What did the police say?

787
00:35:02,100 --> 00:35:03,440
The police said

788
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:05,020
we should pay for the damage

789
00:35:05,790 --> 00:35:07,680
and try to meet all his conditions.

790
00:35:07,710 --> 00:35:10,110
This way, Wanghe might be able to come out

791
00:35:10,140 --> 00:35:11,060
