792
00:35:11,870 --> 00:35:13,470
He's a rotten rogue!

793
00:35:13,490 --> 00:35:15,200
We're to pay him?

794
00:35:15,220 --> 00:35:16,390
How's that possible?

795
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:17,940
S-Stop.

796
00:35:17,970 --> 00:35:19,610
We'll pay him.

797
00:35:19,650 --> 00:35:21,780
T-This is not about money, okay?

798
00:35:22,410 --> 00:35:23,830
Then what do you want to do?

799
00:35:23,870 --> 00:35:25,190
Do you want to make things worse

800
00:35:25,230 --> 00:35:26,750
