804
00:35:32,030 --> 00:35:34,090
We should get him out!

805
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,230
Alright. Alright.

806
00:35:35,230 --> 00:35:36,270
We have to find a way!

807
00:35:36,270 --> 00:35:37,870
Calm down and solve this step by step.

808
00:35:37,870 --> 00:35:38,750
Aren't we

809
00:35:38,750 --> 00:35:40,150
trying to find a solution?

810
00:35:41,380 --> 00:35:41,990
Alright.

811
00:35:41,990 --> 00:35:42,830
Stop crying.

812
00:35:43,510 --> 00:35:44,470
Enough.

813
00:35:45,070 --> 00:35:46,590
It's just detention.

814
00:35:46,630 --> 00:35:47,600
He'll be out in a couple of days.

815
00:35:47,670 --> 00:35:48,470
Everything will be fine.

816
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:54,470
Wanghe was able to go to college.

817
00:35:55,420 --> 00:35:57,810
But because of me…

818
00:35:58,860 --> 00:36:00,100
No matter how indebted you are to him,

819
00:36:00,720 --> 00:36:02,510
you can pay it back bit by bit.

820
00:36:03,870 --> 00:36:06,520
I'm afraid I can't pay it back.

821
00:36:06,550 --> 00:36:08,820
You can if you want to.

822
00:36:10,460 --> 00:36:11,980
Wanghe sees you as his sister.

823
00:36:12,010 --> 00:36:13,230
He stood up for you.

824
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:15,530
We must remember his kindness.

825
00:36:16,070 --> 00:36:16,960
Let me tell you,

826
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:18,590
no matter how it ends for Wanghe,

827
00:36:18,590 --> 00:36:19,910
we'll face it with him.

828
00:36:20,270 --> 00:36:21,270
If he's in debt,

829
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:22,210
we'll pay it together.

830
00:36:22,940 --> 00:36:24,780
Don't pull me!

831
00:36:24,810 --> 00:36:26,720
I have something to do with Haikuo!

832
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:28,850
