841
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:47,350
The law is made to maintain social stability!

842
00:36:47,590 --> 00:36:51,140
That gangster style of settling scores doesn't work!

843
00:36:51,770 --> 00:36:53,170
Then let me ask you, Dad.

844
00:36:53,210 --> 00:36:54,350
Fenghua was bullied.

845
00:36:54,350 --> 00:36:55,110
Should we help her or not?

846
00:36:55,130 --> 00:36:55,890
You should!

847
00:36:55,950 --> 00:36:56,990
Of course you should!

848
00:36:57,900 --> 00:37:00,960
But you should have principles and strategies.

849
00:37:00,990 --> 00:37:02,630
You can't act recklessly, boy!

850
00:37:02,650 --> 00:37:03,170
Right.

851
00:37:03,420 --> 00:37:04,300
Fine.

852
00:37:04,330 --> 00:37:05,720
I'm telling you about this now.

853
00:37:05,860 --> 00:37:08,130
You tell me, how should we get back at that rogue?

854
00:37:09,870 --> 00:37:11,800
Let's find a lawyer to sue him.

855
00:37:11,820 --> 00:37:13,900
Didn't you just say?

856
00:37:13,930 --> 00:37:14,930
