868
00:38:06,990 --> 00:38:09,150
not to simply sweep things under the rug.

869
00:38:09,170 --> 00:38:10,530
You've all watched

870
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:19,160
[Mediator]

871
00:38:10,570 --> 00:38:11,810
the security footage.

872
00:38:13,650 --> 00:38:15,650
Xie Wanghe rushed in and smashed things,

873
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:16,850
but he didn't hurt anyone.

874
00:38:17,470 --> 00:38:19,110
Pang Dahai was the first to get physical.

875
00:38:19,310 --> 00:38:21,610
Xie Wanghe only retaliated after being attacked.

876
00:38:22,270 --> 00:38:23,560
What else could I do?

877
00:38:23,580 --> 00:38:25,140
I was supposed to just watch him smash things?

878
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:27,780
That light alone was very expensive.

879
00:38:28,220 --> 00:38:29,670
If I hadn't stopped him,

880
00:38:29,750 --> 00:38:30,910
I'd have gone bankrupt from the damage.

881
00:38:31,470 --> 00:38:33,300
Regardless of the cause,

882
00:38:33,330 --> 00:38:36,190
the offender committed the crime of picking quarrels and making trouble.

883
00:38:36,270 --> 00:38:37,270
Today, we're here to see

884
00:38:37,270 --> 00:38:39,670
if you can reach an understanding

885
00:38:39,750 --> 00:38:42,150
to minimize the legal consequences of this case.

886
00:38:55,310 --> 00:38:56,200
Alright.

887
00:38:56,300 --> 00:38:58,160
If both parties disagree,

888
00:38:58,200 --> 00:38:59,830
we'll proceed as we should,

889
00:38:59,860 --> 00:39:01,860
with detention or sentence as necessary.

890
00:39:02,520 --> 00:39:03,700
Think it through.

891
00:39:11,870 --> 00:39:14,510
Can I speak to him privately for a moment?

892
00:39:18,690 --> 00:39:19,810
Thank you.

893
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:36,960
This time,

894
00:39:37,790 --> 00:39:39,510
it was indeed my son's fault.

895
00:39:40,740 --> 00:39:42,220
I apologize to you.

896
00:39:44,430 --> 00:39:45,890
Apologizing now

897
00:39:47,130 --> 00:39:48,730
is a bit late, isn't it?

898
00:39:55,580 --> 00:39:56,900
The reason

899
00:39:57,620 --> 00:39:59,240
why he beat you,

900
00:40:00,460 --> 00:40:03,540
you know better than anyone, don't you?

901
00:40:04,180 --> 00:40:05,070
What do you mean?

902
00:40:05,510 --> 00:40:06,860
Fenghua

903
00:40:06,970 --> 00:40:08,310
is still in school.

904
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:11,110
How could you do such a thing to a young girl?

905
00:40:11,380 --> 00:40:12,540
Don't you think

906
00:40:14,410 --> 00:40:15,660
it's despicable?

907
00:40:19,140 --> 00:40:20,750
W-What did I do?

908
00:40:21,140 --> 00:40:22,080
Playing dumb, huh?

909
00:40:24,300 --> 00:40:26,030
You're a man.

910
00:40:26,520 --> 00:40:28,240
Just own up to what you did.

911
00:40:28,790 --> 00:40:29,670
What did I do?

912
00:40:29,690 --> 00:40:31,050
What should I own up to?

913
00:40:31,890 --> 00:40:32,640
Let me tell you.

914
00:40:32,660 --> 00:40:33,900
Don't talk nonsense here.

915
00:40:33,940 --> 00:40:35,080
This is the police station.

916
00:40:35,150 --> 00:40:36,420
I'll sue you for defamation.

917
00:40:45,110 --> 00:40:45,920
Anyway,

918
00:40:47,960 --> 00:40:49,810
he's my only son.

919
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:53,800
You've met me

920
00:40:54,240 --> 00:40:56,730
and my husband.

921
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:58,520
Both of us are very ordinary.

922
00:40:58,540 --> 00:40:59,500
In this life,

923
00:41:00,890 --> 00:41:03,140
we only hope our son can

924
00:41:03,910 --> 00:41:04,910
make something of himself.

925
00:41:06,430 --> 00:41:09,710
If you crush our only hope,

926
00:41:11,380 --> 00:41:12,860
don't blame us

927
00:41:13,030 --> 00:41:14,500
for dragging you down.

928
00:41:16,250 --> 00:41:17,550
Are you threatening me?

929
00:41:17,570 --> 00:41:18,800
I'm not threatening you.

930
00:41:19,610 --> 00:41:20,730
I'm negotiating with you.

931
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:23,630
I'm not asking you to put yourself in our shoes.

932
00:41:23,990 --> 00:41:25,180
I'm just asking you

933
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:28,930
not to ruin the futures

934
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:31,460
of both our families.

935
00:41:35,950 --> 00:41:37,390
I'm begging you.

936
00:41:52,620 --> 00:41:53,660
Let's do the math.

937
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:56,460
[Mediator]

938
00:41:54,600 --> 00:41:55,660
Well,

939
00:41:55,710 --> 00:41:56,680
medical treatment

940
00:41:56,710 --> 00:41:58,300
has cost about 30,000 yuan.

941
00:41:59,700 --> 00:42:01,870
Recovering from these injuries

942
00:42:02,110 --> 00:42:03,310
will cost quite a bit too, right?

943
00:42:04,910 --> 00:42:08,070
And the smashed cameras and computers,

944
00:42:08,070 --> 00:42:10,630
all these odds and ends,

945
00:42:10,630 --> 00:42:11,760
if you add them up…

946
00:42:14,180 --> 00:42:15,300
100,000 yuan.

947
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,230
That should settle this matter.

948
00:42:16,270 --> 00:42:16,980
100,000?

949
00:42:18,310 --> 00:42:19,960
Why don't you just rob a bank?

950
00:42:21,560 --> 00:42:23,130
100,000 it is.

951
00:42:23,160 --> 00:42:25,040
Let's sign the agreement now.

952
00:42:26,380 --> 00:42:27,600
Are you sure?

953
00:42:27,630 --> 00:42:28,670
Wait.

954
00:42:28,700 --> 00:42:29,580
Listen.

955
00:42:29,610 --> 00:42:31,400
It must be paid in full at once.

956
00:42:32,050 --> 00:42:33,290
Paid in full at once?

957
00:42:33,310 --> 00:42:34,240
You're really pushing it, aren't you?

958
00:42:34,270 --> 00:42:35,320
No problem.

959
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:36,450
If you hadn't done that despicable thing…

960
00:42:36,510 --> 00:42:37,070
No problem.

961
00:42:37,070 --> 00:42:38,570
could my son have beaten you up?

962
00:42:38,770 --> 00:42:39,330
Alright, stop.

963
00:42:39,370 --> 00:42:40,610
This is the police station.

964
00:42:40,640 --> 00:42:42,670
This is the police station!

965
00:42:43,350 --> 00:42:43,950
Stop yelling.

966
00:42:43,990 --> 00:42:45,910
It's already settled. Stop arguing.

967
00:42:45,910 --> 00:42:46,990
Do you know where you are?

968
00:42:46,990 --> 00:42:47,990
Alright. Don't listen to him.

969
00:42:48,030 --> 00:42:49,350
I can make the decision on this matter.

970
00:42:49,390 --> 00:42:50,270
You can't!

971
00:42:50,310 --> 00:42:51,150
Don't get yourself arrested!

972
00:42:51,150 --> 00:42:51,990
It's 100,000 yuan!

973
00:42:52,030 --> 00:42:52,790
Shut up!

974
00:42:58,110 --> 00:42:58,630
I'll sign.
